              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>We will write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{A}\downarrow {\mathcal {U}} :\equiv  \mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (X:\mathcal {U}\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (X:\mathcal {U}\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (X:\mathcal {U}\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (X:\mathcal {U}\right )\mathclose {}}}}{A\to  X}]]></fr:tex> for the type of <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">reflection algebras</fr:link> under <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>; given two reflection algebras <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X,Y:{A}\downarrow {\mathcal {U}}]]></fr:tex> we will write <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (X\multimap  Y\right )\mathclose {}} :\equiv  \mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (f:X\to  Y\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (f:X\to  Y\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (f:X\to  Y\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (f:X\to  Y\right )\mathclose {}}}} {\eta _{Y}} \sim _{A\to  Y} {f\circ  \eta _{X}}]]></fr:tex> for the type of <html:em>homomorphisms</html:em> of <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">reflection algebras</fr:link>.</html:p>
