              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X:{A}\downarrow {\mathcal {U}}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">reflection algebra</fr:link>; a <html:em>displayed reflection algebra</html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y]]></fr:tex> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is defined to be a dependent type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bar {U}Y : X \to  \mathcal {U}]]></fr:tex> together with a dependent function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\bar {\eta }_{Y} : \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (a:A\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (a:A\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (a:A\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{{\mathopen {}\left (a:A\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\bar {U}Y{\mathopen {}\left (\eta _{X}a\right )\mathclose {}}}.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
