              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Given a <fr:link href="/jms-003R/" title="Displayed reflection algebra" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003R/" display-uri="jms-003R" type="local">displayed reflection algebra</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y]]></fr:tex> over a <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">reflection algebra</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X:{A}\downarrow {\mathcal {U}}]]></fr:tex>, we may define the <html:em>total reflection algebra</html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\widetilde {Y}:{A}\downarrow {\mathcal {U}}]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y]]></fr:tex> as follows:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {array}{l}
    U\widetilde {Y} :\equiv  \mathchoice {\textstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (x:Ux\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\textstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (x:Ux\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (x:Ux\right )\mathclose {}}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \sum _{{\mathopen {}\left (x:Ux\right )\mathclose {}}}}Y[x] \\
    \eta _{\widetilde {Y}}a :\equiv  {\mathopen {}\left (\eta _{X}a,\bar {\eta }_{Y}a\right )\mathclose {}}
  \end {array}
]]></fr:tex>
                <html:p>The projection function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{U\widetilde {Y}}\xrightarrow {{\pi _1}}{UX}]]></fr:tex> extends to a <fr:link href="/jms-003O/" title="Reflection algebras and homomorphisms" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-003O/" display-uri="jms-003O" type="local">homomorphism of reflection algebras</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\pi _{Y}:\widetilde {Y}\multimap  X]]></fr:tex> as follows:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {array}{l}
    \pi _{Y} {\mathopen {}\left (x,y\right )\mathclose {}} :\equiv  x \\
    \alpha _{\pi _{Y}} a :\equiv  \mathsf {refl}
  \end {array}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
